posts.post_title: WTB: E90-1 American Caramel Buck Jordan (Jordon)
posts.post_content: PM if you have or know of one!

[quote name="MJRaider" post=2504869]PM if you have or know of one![/QUOTE]


I don’t have a spare—just the one in my collection—but a heads up that may help your searches. Though PSA slabs this card as Buck Jordan, that’s an error on their part. This is 2x NL home run champ Tim Jordan, who was never known as Buck. I suspect PSA had Tim confused with a 1930s player.

If you ever wanted to read way too much about the error, here you go. [url]https://sabrbaseballcards.blog/2020/03/08/the-original-err-jordan/[/url]


Jason
